title: Impregnate Me Causa My Husband Can't
alternative_title: Otto no Oshiego ni Kaihatsu Sareru Moteamashita Karada
status: Otto no Oshiego ni Kaihatsu Sareru Moteamashita Karada
description:
Description :
        Megumi, who had been married to her husband for several years, was saddened that he was unable to produce enough sperm to get her pregnant, so she decided to get a sperm donation. But she never expected that the sperm donor would be someone she knew.
